https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/137341/', '', 'Clonazepam, Cenobamate, Carbamazepine, Fosphenytoin, Phenytoin, Primidone, Phenobarbital, Stiripentol, Suvorexant, Triazolam, Flurazepam, More', 'Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Tryptophan', 1767369485);
